      | C_AcctSchema_ID | M_Product_ID | M_CostElement_ID               | CurrentCostPrice | CurrentQty |
      | acctSchema      | product      | AveragePO,MovingAverageInvoice | 1000000 CHF      | 10 PCE     |
    
    
